    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      This website is hosted on <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> (Cloudflare, Inc., 101 Townsend St, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). When you visit this website, Cloudflare processes the connection data required to deliver the page (IP address, requested URL, date and time). This processing is based on Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in providing a secure and efficient website).
    </p>
    <p>
      Cloudflare is certified under the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework. No personal data is stored beyond what is necessary for the technical delivery of the page. Cloudflare acts as a data processor under a Data Processing Agreement (DPA).
    </p>
    <p>
      Cloudflare may use <strong>Cloudflare RUM (Real User Monitoring)</strong> to measure page load performance. This collects technical metrics (page load times, browser type, screen size) without cookies, without personal data, and without cross-site tracking.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      This website uses <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> to collect anonymous usage statistics. Cloudflare Web Analytics:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> use cookies</li>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> store IP addresses</li>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> use fingerprinting or cross-site tracking</li>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> collect personal data</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Since no personal data is processed, no consent is required under GDPR. The legal basis is Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in understanding website usage).
    </p>

    <h2>No Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This website does not set any cookies. No consent banner is necessary.
    </p>

