    <p>
      This website contains links to external platforms (GitHub, Dev.to, Hashnode, Twitter, LinkedIn). When you follow these links, you are subject to the privacy policies of those platforms. I have no control over the data they collect.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request information about any personal data processed (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion of your data (Art. 16, 17 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Restrict or object to processing (Art. 18, 21 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Since this website does not collect personal data beyond what Cloudflare requires for technical delivery, these rights are unlikely to apply in practice. If you have questions, contact me at kevin.mauel2@gmail.com.
    </p>
